Number Counter
Create a GUI application titled "Number Counter", that contains a single label and two buttons.
The following is the detailed list of components:
  • Label
    o Name - countLabel
    o Default Text - "0"
  • Button
    o Name - increaseButton
    o Text - "Increase"
    o Functionality - Clicking this button should increment the value displayed in the countLabel by 1.
  • Button
    o Name - decreaseButton
    o Text - "Decrease"
    o Functionality - Clicking this button should decrement the value displayed in the countLabel by 1.
  
  Note:
  • Use setName() to set the names of the components. Variable names do not count as
  the name
